lead_paragraph: WASTE PAPER--Parties desirous of giving the largest price for Waste Paper, are earnestly Irequested to make the speedlest application for bits of theo New Austrian Loan. Persons may be accommodated to the amount of at least seven millions. Come early. No bigotry! All religions taken in.
